data.title: Shelley Conn: Movies, Photos, Videos, News, Biography & Birthday
data.meta_description: Shelley Conn: Check out the list of all Shelley Conn movies along with photos, videos, biography and birthday. Also find latest Shelley Conn news on Times of India.
data.text:
Superhero web-series 'The Boys' releases teaser for spin-off series 'Gen V'

IANS / Jul 22, 2023, 15:08 (IST)

The web-series 'The Boys' is getting a spin-off called 'Gen V', which will explore the training of the first generation of superheroes to know about Compound V.

'Gen V': 'The Boys' spinoff gets a release date

etimes.in / Jul 21, 2023, 18:07 (IST)

Spin off series from The Boys called Gen V will be releasing in September , it boasts a stellar starcast with Jessie T Usher, Colby Minifie, and PJ Byrne, reprising their roles from 'The Boys'.

OTT's 'The Boys' spin-off show is titled 'Gen V'

PTI / Jul 16, 2022, 12:55 (IST)

Streaming service's upcoming 'The Boys' spin-off series has been titled 'Gen V'. The young adult series is described as a "part college show, part Hunger Games" project with all the "heart, satire, and raunch of 'The Boys'", the streaming service said in a statement.

'Bridgerton' Season 2 trailer unveils what happens when duty and desire conflict

ANI / Mar 10, 2022, 10:52 (IST)

Netflix, on Wednesday, unveiled the trailer for the upcoming second season of the romantic drama series 'Bridgerton', which focuses on the love triangle between Anthony Bridgerton (Jonathan Bailey) and sisters Edwina (Charithra Chandran) and Kate Sharma (Simone Ashley).

Hamish Linklater boards season 2 of 'Gen V'

PTI / Jun 05, 2024, 13:30 (IST)

Renowned Hollywood Actor Hamish Linklater joins the cast of 'Gen V' as Cipher, the newly-appointed Dean of Godolkin University in the world of 'The Boys'. The series follows the training of first-generation superheroes at the university to uncover the truth about Compound V, a mysterious substance granting powers to humans.

Diane Kruger, Jo Joyner to lead psychological thriller 'Little Disasters'

PTI / Jun 11, 2024, 15:19 (IST)

Actors Diane Kruger and Jo Joyner will feature in 'Little Disasters', a psychological thriller series on Paramount+. Based on Sarah Vaughan's novel, the show explores female friendships and motherhood through four women with different due dates.

'Gen V' production delayed due to sudden demise of Chance Perdomo

ANI / Mar 31, 2024, 16:54 (IST)

Chance Perdomo, who worked in TV series such as 'Gen V' and 'Chilling Adventures of Sabrina' has passed away at the age of 27. In light of Perdomo's passing, the start of Season 2 production on 'Gen V' has been delayed indefinitely, reported Deadline.

'The Boys' spin-off 'Gen V' RENEWED for second season; cast and crew to return to tell 'bold stories'

etimes.in / Oct 20, 2023, 11:23 (IST)

"Gen V", the spin-off series of "The Boys", has been renewed for a second season. The announcement came just weeks after the show premiered on Prime Video. The show has been a success, becoming the number one series on Prime Video in over 130 countries. The second season will continue to explore the world of superheroes at Godolkin University, delving into the ups and downs of the young supes as they navigate popularity and uncover sinister secrets.

The Boys spinoff series Gen V introduces a new breed of supes starring Jaz Sinclair, Chance Perdomo, Lizze Broadway- Details Inside

etimes.in / Aug 23, 2023, 21:35 (IST)

The spinoff of The Boys, titled Gen V, takes place at Godolkin University, a prestigious superhero college where students train to become the next generation of heroes. The series follows a group of young supes as they navigate college life while facing explosive situations and uncovering a sinister plot.

Gen V trailer: The Boys spinoff series introduces new generation of Supes and their super powers

etimes.in / Sep 07, 2023, 17:37 (IST)

The makers of 'Gen V' finally launched the trailer of the series that is a spin-off of the popular dark comedy, satirical superhero show 'The Boys'. The series aims to further explore a new generation of Supes, in greater detail.

'Bridgerton' Season 2 to star Rupert Evans in a key role

PTI / May 28, 2021, 21:03 (IST)

'Charmed' star Rupert Evans has been roped in to play a pivotal role in the second season of Netflix's runaway hit series "Bridgerton". According to Entertainment Weekly, Evans will play Edmund Bridgerton in the upcoming season of the Regency London drama. Edmund Bridgerton is late husband to Violet Bridgerton (Ruth Gemmell) and father to the entire Bridgerton clan.

'Bridgerton' season 2 to arrive in March

PTI / Dec 26, 2021, 15:28 (IST)

The much-awaited second season of the runaway series 'Bridgerton' will premiere on March 25, the streamer has announced. Based on Julia Quinn's bestselling novels, the show is produced by media magnate Shonda Rhimes' Shondaland banner.

Confirmed! 'Bridgerton' is returning with seasons 3 and 4

TNN & Agencies / Apr 14, 2021, 11:00 (IST)

Just as 'Bridgerton' fans were rejoicing about season two going on floors, Lady Whistledown, spilled the tea late last night and revealed that the drama has been renewed for seasons three and four as well.
